<p><b>How do you cite a PDF in APA 7th edition with two authors?</b> Author Surname, First Initial. Second Initial., & Author Surname, First Initial. Second Initial. (Year).</p>
<p><b>How do you cite a file in APA 7th edition?</b> Author, A. A. (Date). Title of document. http://... If an online document has a corporate author, then that entity is assumed to be the publisher and the name of the website is omitted.</p>